A few tips: 
* Exercise. It doesn’t have to be for long, but it is one of the BEST things to help fight depression.

* Vitamin D3. Studies have shown high doses help fight depression.

media.altText:
5  stages of despair:
🫖You forgot your tea & it has gone cold. You mourn it & make a fresh cup.
🫖You microwave the cold tea.
🫖Finding a fruit fly in your tea, you throw it away & make a fresh cup.
🫖You remove the fruit fly with a spoon & drink the tea.
🫖You just don't bother & drink the tea!

Credit: @ShidaKatz

rawContent:
#depression

It's the creeping nature of it
Like some horror movie
But it climbs out ur soul
Not ur tv
Lingers over ur shoulder
As u paint
Hangs from the ceiling
As u sleep
Creeps behind u thro the woods
Corrupting ur joys
Enveloping ur life lines
And NO ONE sees it
But u
#poem
